*πίπτω, πέτω / piptō  petō /  pip'-to, pet'-o
=== Etymology ===

The first is a reduplicated and contracted form of the second (which occurs only as an alternate in certain tenses); probably akin to [[πέτομαι]] {{GG|4072}} through the idea of alighting; 
=== Verb ===
to fall (literally of figuratively): - [[fail]], [[fall]] (down), [[light]] on.